name: Grape Solar 265-Watt Polycrystalline PV Solar Panel Bundle

The Grape Solar 265-Watt Polycrystalline PV Solar Panel uses high efficiency solar cells (approximately 19%) made from quality silicon material for high module conversion efficiency, long term output stability, and reliability. Virtually maintenance free.
